遇到相同的问题，最后解决了。
服务器用的是Nginx，配置有rewrite导致。
这里给个简单的可行基础配置：
`
http {
# ShowDoc base config
server {
    listen       8080;
    server_name  api.com;
    root   /usr/local/showdoc;

    access_log  logs/api.access.log;
    error_log   logs/api.error.log;

    location / {
        index  index.html index.htm index.php;
    }

    location ~ \.php$ {
        root        html;
        fastcgi_pass   127.0.0.1:9000;
        include        fastcgi_params;
        fastcgi_index  index.php;
        fastcgi_param  SCRIPT_FILENAME  /usr/local/showdoc$fastcgi_script_name; 
    }
}

}
`
